metadata.description: Data Type: Subsistence/Traditional Knowledge;   Automation of the Ahtna native routes as provided by James Kari in Tatl'ahwt'aenn nenn, the headwaters People's Country. This is a layer in the Copper River Native Association Subsistence Database 1995. (Record#061)
